<li id="cite_note-39"><b><a href="#cite_ref-39" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBarak-Glantz.2C_I.L..2C_E.H._Johnson1983">Barak-Glantz, I.L., E.H. Johnson (1983). <i>Comparative criminology</i>. Sage.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Comparative+criminology&amp;rft.aulast=Barak-Glantz%2C+I.L.%2C+E.H.+Johnson&amp;rft.au=Barak-Glantz%2C+I.L.%2C+E.H.+Johnson&amp;rft.date=1983&amp;rft.pub=Sage&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Criminology"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><a name="Bibliography" id="Bibliography"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Criminology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bibliography</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/en:Introduction_to_Sociology" class="extiw" title="b:en:Introduction to Sociology">Wikibooks: Introduction to sociology</a></li>
